# Multi-seed: dashboard (stranica "Multi-seed analiza", tab Krive treninga) cita
# SAMO training_history_*.json po seedu (~64 KB ukupno). Sve ostalo u runs/
# (checkpointi ~37 MB, per-seed figure/CSV/logovi) se NE commituje; regenerise se
# sa scripts/10_run_multi_seed.py, a best modeli idu u GitHub Release.
outputs/runs/**
!outputs/runs/**/
!outputs/runs/**/training_history_*.json

# Streamlit log i privremeni radni fajlovi
outputs/streamlit.log
_*.txt

